|               |                 Projection: catalog_returns.cr_returning_customer_sk AS ctr_customer_sk, customer_address.ca_state AS ctr_state, sum(catalog_returns.cr_return_amt_inc_tax) AS ctr_total_return                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               